  "title": "Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibility including but not limited to:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ferry workers to work site on time and back to dormitory.</li>\n  <li>Take responsibility and care for company's vehicle.</li>\n  <li>Carry out daily routine safety check and maintenance of vehicle</li>\n  <li>Collect materials from supplier and send to sites.</li>\n  <li>Assist to clear dump and scrap from sites as and when necessary.</li>\n  <li>Site coordination &amp; arrangement.</li>\n  <li>Report site situation to superior as and when necessary.</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties as and when assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess valid driving license with proven safe record</li>\n  <li>At least 2-3 year of relevant driving experience</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude, able to work as a team</li>\n  <li>Prior working experience in construction working environment is an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to follow work instruction and work according to the schedule/task arrangement</li>\n  <li>Able to perform duties beyond designated working hours</li>\n</ul>",
